===== Screen item =====

This class is designed to work with screen items. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:screenitem:object#screen_item|Screen item]]

Available methods: \\
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:screenitem:create|screenitem.create]]'' - creating new screen items
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:screenitem:delete|screenitem.delete]]'' - deleting screen items
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:screenitem:get|screenitem.get]]'' - retrieving screen items
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:screenitem:update|screenitem.update]]'' - updating screen items
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:screenitem:updatebyposition|screenitem.updatebyposition]]'' - updating screen items in a specific screen cell